title: Grateful Dead Live at Nassau Coliseum on 1984-04-29
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Friend Of The Devil, CC Rider, Bird Song, Hell In A Bucket, West L.A. Fadeaway, Cassidy, Ramble On Rose, Let It Grow

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider-> Samson & Delilah, Terrapin Station-> Don't Need Love-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Day Job

reviews.review_text: Extraordinary. Thank u So Much finding this made my day. There is a long jam after Terrapin, absolutely interesting and excellent in my opionion, before don't need love, been listening t the old Audience TAPE forever, since it happened, I always forward it to that jam, but now if we got it allover again, I'll be like I never heard it before, and we just got the word DeadCo etc is playin at Nassau November 5 and 6, 2019. Not the best show ever but the uniqueness, just happened to be that old at that time...(16).!!!!! Thanks again. those were the days...of 25 minute drums/space.
